      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. It\u2019s super smooth on the road and ready for its next adventure. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how well it\u2019s been kept. Swing by and take a look!",
